    {
        "content": "<p>from these:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">localized</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"notation `‚ü™`x`, `y`‚ü´` := @inner ‚Ñù _ _ x y\"</span> <span class=\"k\">in</span> <span class=\"n\">real_inner_product_space</span>\n<span class=\"n\">localized</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"notation `‚ü™`x`, `y`‚ü´` := @inner ‚ÑÇ _ _ x y\"</span> <span class=\"k\">in</span> <span class=\"n\">complex_inner_product_space</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>it follows that you can <code>open_locale real_inner_product_space</code> to say you want the unadorned notation to refer to the real inner product</p>",
